				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2012/11/sam-harris-on-the-brink-of-having-an-intellectual-nde/" title="Permalink to Sam Harris on the Brink of Having an (Intellectual) NDE?" rel="bookmark">Sam Harris on the Brink of Having an (Intellectual) NDE?</a></h3>
