			<div id="post-4262" class="hentry p2 post publish author-c4chaos category-science y2012 m10 d17 h03 alt">
				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2012/10/sam-harris-vs-dr-eben-alexander-on-nde/" title="Permalink to Sam Harris vs. Dr. Eben Alexander on NDE" rel="bookmark">Sam Harris vs. Dr. Eben Alexander on NDE</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2012-10-17T22:38:30+0000">Wednesday, October 17th, 2012</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
<p>Last week Newsweek published an excerpt of Dr. Eben Alexander&#8217;s book, &#8220;Proof of Heaven&#8220;, as its cover story. I&#8217;m already familiar with Dr. Eben Alexander&#8217;s NDE (Near-Death Experience) case because I&#8217;ve listened to his interview on Skeptiko last year. However, I don&#8217;t know the exact details of his case and the &#8220;proof&#8221; that he offers [&hellip;]</p>
